\caption{Multiset encode}\label{alg:roc-encode} Given a multiset $\M = \{x_1, \dots, x_n\}$ with $m$ unique symbols Assume encoding with $P_X$ has worst-case complexity per-symbol of $\Omega(P^	ext{enc}_X)$ Initialize an ANS state $s_0$, and $\overline\M_1 = \M$ \For{$i = 1, \dots, n$}{ 
l $(s_i', z_i) = \decode(s_{i-1})$ with $P_{Z_i \g \overline\M_i}$ 	cp{$\Omega(\log m)$} 
l $\overline\M_{i+1} = \overline\M_i\setminus\{z_i\}$ 	cp{$\Omega(\log m)$} 
l $s_i = \encode(s_i', z_i)$ with $P_X(z_i)$ 	cp{$\Omega(P^	ext{enc}_X)$} } \Return $s_n$

